[174.106062, "o", "\r\n  Based on Sprint 1 retro, the PO Agent will receive:\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mImprovements to apply:\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m1.\u001b[0m Add competitor rate comparison\r\n       \u001b[2mFlag anomalies vs market average, not just hotel history\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m2.\u001b[0m Seasonal decomposition\r\n       \u001b[2mSeparate trend + seasonality before z-score (avoid false positives)\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m3.\u001b[0m REST API endpoint\r\n       \u001b[2mPOST /anomalies with date range filter, FastAPI\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m4.\u001b[0m Dashboard data export\r\n       \u001b[2mJSON output for revenue management team dashboard\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mTo run Sprint 2:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m$ python3 orchestrator.py \"Improve the charging optimizer: add departure\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m  deadline, multi-truck scheduling, input validation, and CLI\"\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
